## Technical Stack

- **Frontend Framework**: Next.js with React 19
- **UI Library**: shadcn/ui with Tailwind CSS V4
- **Programming Language**: TypeScript 5.0+
- **State Management**: Zustand (Can use `useState` etc... BUT: No other state management lib!)
- **Form Handling**: React Hook Form with Zod validation (Form component in `/app/components/ui/form.tsx`)
- **API**: REST endpoints with Next.js API `Route Handlers` (Do not use Next.js `actions`)